{
  "stem": "4284.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 128,
      "text": "General Patton had sent tanks up the hill, which Buchenwald was on a high mountain-- no other way to get up there except one railroad facility and a small street.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 129,
      "text": "And he had sent tanks up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 130,
      "text": "And on the tank, he allowed a Yiddish, Polish, whatever speaking soldier to be there, which was a high risk position to be in.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 131,
      "text": "And the only way that they could make any sense out of them not being attacked-- and being misrecognized, is right in front, they painted the Star of David.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 132,
      "text": "And so we realized that were being liberated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 133,
      "text": "We were liberated on the 11th of April, 1945, as I said, by Patton's Third Army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 134,
      "text": "And we could not do anything to help ourselves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 135,
      "text": "We were too weak.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 136,
      "text": "Well, it was immediately followed-- the troops were followed by the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 137,
      "text": "And they took those that seemed to have the best chance of survival.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 138,
      "text": "It's-- in the medical field, it's called triaging.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 139,
      "text": "Those that were too far gone, to give them help was of little value.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 140,
      "text": "So the ones that looked a little stronger, which turned out to be the younger ones, they put us into the, the barracks that the German SS, the guards, had occupied.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 141,
      "text": "And they gave us some minor food, milk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 142,
      "text": "And we were-- hungry isn't the word.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 143,
      "text": "And we're all complaining that we're not getting enough food now that it's available.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 144,
      "text": "The tragedy was that we lost over 3,000 people because of food after the liberation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 145,
      "text": "We were too weak to participate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 146,
      "text": "But others were strong enough to go down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 147,
      "text": "There were some Russian prisoners of war, which were given a little bit more food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 148,
      "text": "So they a little bit more strength than the rest of us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 149,
      "text": "And they had also put away certain things.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
